=======================
gedit 2.3.2 - "Waiting"
=======================

Enhancements
============

- Metadata manager (Paolo Maggi)
- Highlight Mode submenu (Paolo)
- Encoding status bar (Paolo)
- Always show Cursor Position and Overwrite Mode (Paolo)


Fixes
=====

- Fixed "Requires" in gedit.pc.in (Paolo)
- Removed statusbar_show_cursor_position and statusbar_show_overwrite_mode keys
  from the .schema file (Paolo) 
- Bug #105378 - View > Customize Toolbar options should be changed (Paolo)
- Added a KOI8-R encoding (alexhack AT inbox DOT ru)
- Replaced deprecated calls gtk_timeout_remove and gtk_timeout_add (Yogeesh MB)


